						<div class="postbody">It's dependent on how you want to define emulation. I'd say yes, by my own use of the term, but I think this is a grey area. I can't imagine it not being clear what someone means by the context though. I can't really think of a situation where it would matter whether you'd define it to be an emulation or not.</div>

